title: New: Jelly Jells – B€/\UT!FU{_
body:
Not much is know about **[Jelly Jells](http://www.facebook.com/jellyjells)**, apart from a quote that’s been well publicised by all who have written about him.

“**Jelly Jells** is a half black, half italian son of a prostitute. He is a musician, magician, inventor, aesthete, dreamer, doer and believer!”

 Not a bad introduction to an artist that has so far only released one solitary mp3. But what a tune it is. Sitting firmly between **Outcast** and **TV On The Radio** in terms of tone, his debut release is an uplifting, stomach churning, eccentric, bitter and most of all groove filled slice of break-up pop.

Stream the track below, and thanks to our bros at **[Get Of The Coast](http://getoffthecoast.blogspot.com)** for the heads up.

 [Jelly Jells- B€/\\UT!FU{\_](http://soundcloud.com/jellyjells/jelly-jells) by [jellyjells](http://soundcloud.com/jellyjells)
